<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c2">(الدعاس ص ٣١، اللحجي ص ٣٨)</span> .<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
